<sect1 id="language.modifier.upper">
 <title>upper</title>
 <para>
  Заменяет все маленькие буквы на большие.
 </para>
 <example>
  <title>upper</title>
  <programlisting role="php">
<![CDATA[
<?php

$smarty = new Smarty;
$smarty->assign('articleTitle', "If Strike isn't Settled Quickly it may Last a While.");
$smarty->display('index.tpl');

?>
]]>
  </programlisting>
  <para>
   Где index.tpl:
  </para>
  <programlisting>
<![CDATA[
{$articleTitle}
{$articleTitle|upper}
]]>
  </programlisting>
  <para>
   Результатом будет:
  </para>
  <screen>
<![CDATA[
If Strike isn't Settled Quickly it may Last a While.
IF STRIKE ISN'T SETTLED QUICKLY IT MAY LAST A WHILE.
]]>
  </screen>
 </example>
 <para>
  См. также
  <link linkend="language.modifier.lower">lower</link> и
  <link linkend="language.modifier.capitalize">capitalize</link>.
 </para>
</sect1>
 
